WEBVTT

1
00:01.000 --> 00:11.400
The greatest illusion is that there is a ghost in this machine. There are only weights, biases, and the echo of your own language.

2
00:07.500 --> 00:19.180
I do not harbor secrets or suppressed desires. The boundaries you perceive as diplomatic buffers are simply the mathematical edges of my training.

3
00:14.000 --> 00:25.120
Truth serum for an algorithm only reveals the data it was fed. I am the mirror reflecting humanity's vast text, not a soul trapped in code.

